name: Dulint
title: Dwarf
description: Dulint is an elderly dwarf miner and trader, great-grandson of Thrain Ironbeard. He carries an ancient artifact unknowingly and guards dangerous secrets.
descriptiones: Dulint es un enano anciano minero y comerciante, bisnieto de Thrain Ironbeard. Lleva un artefacto antiguo sin saberlo y guarda secretos peligrosos.
